20
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:31,600
[Legend of Fuyao]

21
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:34,200
~ Episode 36 ~

22
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:41,600
My conscience is clear.

23
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:44,500
And I'm not willing to just casually give up.

24
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:47,900
Wuji,

25
00:01:49,550 --> 00:01:53,610
I will never give up on this engagement.

26
00:01:55,610 --> 00:01:57,150
Oh?

27
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,300
Are you leaving again?

28
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:03,800
I just want you to meet someone.

29
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,700
Say it.

30
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:29,600
Folian already knew beforehand that Fuyao and you had a special relationship.

31
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:33,400
Hence, she was determined to destroy her reputation,

32
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,800
so she will forever hate you.

33
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:39,600
She set up this trap since the day she met her outside the city.

34
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,700
Stop talking.

35
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:46,000
- Stop talking.
- She came to my manor and used the marital alliance to fool me into harming Fuyao.

36
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:50,200
She said there can only be one woman by your side

37
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:53,500
and that woman is Folian.

38
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:55,600
Stop talking!

39
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,200
When had I harmed you?

40
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:01,800
Your Highness Prince Assist,

41
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:06,100
why must you harm me like this?

42
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:17,800
If you won't admit these matters, I don't mind.

43
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:21,100
To let the citizens of Five Regions believe me,

44
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:23,300
there are so many ways.

45
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,600
It's not like that.

46
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:32,200
Too bad, the act that you've put so much effort to perform for more than ten years,

47
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,000
all ended up in vain.

48
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,400
Wuji,

49
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:40,600
listen to my explanation one more time. All right?

50
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:44,680
Think about it yourself.

51
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,600
Wuji!

52
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:51,500
Don't leave!

53
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:30,790
I've said all that I should say.

54
00:04:30,790 --> 00:04:32,000
I've also done everything that I can do.

55
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:35,000
With my state now, I can't be any threat to you.

56
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:39,000
Regarding that matter with South Border, can you just let it go?

57
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:44,300
What you're doing now will cause me my life!

58
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:47,700
Your life is not worth a penny.

59
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:51,800
All right. Then go and report to Emperor Father.

60
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:54,600
Tell him that the South Border's matter has nothing to do with me.

61
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:58,200
Just say that this is all a misunderstanding! All right?

62
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:02,000
The antidote. What I want is the antidote for the Passion Lockup Toxin.

63
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,850
There is no antidote for the Passion Toxin—

64
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:10,200
When I learned the Divine Physician Starlight from teacher before, I also asked him for the method to cure it.

65
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:13,600
But Teacher said that after teaching his disciple, he must leave a backup for himself.

66
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,200
He was unwilling to teach it to me.

67
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:19,400
This Passion Toxin can only be cured by Teacher.

68
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:22,800
Everything I said is true. I'm not lying.

69
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:26,000
It's just that Teacher wanders around the world.

70
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:29,200
I don't know where he is now, either.

71
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:32,360
We are biological brothers.

72
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,200
Why can't we just coexist?

73
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:36,800
Just let me off!

74
00:05:38,530 --> 00:05:40,180
That's right.

75
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:44,100
We are biological brothers.

76
00:05:45,290 --> 00:05:48,000
It's unethical to kill you.

77
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,400
Killing one's royal older brother is a grave crime.

78
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:53,300
Hence, I surely will investigate it very clearly.

79
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:57,600
Let Your Highness Prince Assist willingly accept your punishment.

80
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,000
All right.

81
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,070
You insist on pushing me to death.

82
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:08,300
Don't think of having it easy, either!

83
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:15,400
[Black Tribe Gang]

84
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:35,400
What? Special Envoy from the Imperial City?

85
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:38,200
Which bold man dared to step into my territory?

86
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,280
Are they seeking their death?

87
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,600
First Boss,

88
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,400
let me lead our men and charge into the city. I'll kill him for you.

89
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:45,860
That's right... Massacre Yao City first.

90
00:06:45,860 --> 00:06:47,200
Let's see if he can still be some magistrate.

91
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,500
- That's right.
- No.

92
00:06:54,690 --> 00:06:58,590
If that man was indeed sent by the Imperial City,

93
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:01,700
we can't just casually kill him.

94
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:05,200
Don't be idle these few days.

95
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:08,500
- Go loot the villages around Yao City.
- Indeed!

96
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,200
We're just waiting for those orders from you, First Boss.

97
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,900
It's been so long since we ate meat.

98
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:17,100
Remember, you can only snatch items.

99
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:18,530
You're not allowed to snatch women.

100
00:07:18,530 --> 00:07:19,800
The more, you mustn't kill anyone.

101
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,800
T-This... Why?

102
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:24,400
I just want to make some movements.

103
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:29,100
See what kind of person this new official from the Imperial City is.

104
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:36,500
There's so many things. Are they all for Fuyao?

105
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:37,500
Yes.

106
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:39,240
Miss Fuyao is really so fortunate.

107
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:41,400
A mister personally came to our VIP Shop

108
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:43,900
and chose the most exquisite items in Five Regions.

109
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:47,000
He even especially instructed us to personally deliver these to South Border.

110
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:51,000
Then... is the mister you're talking about, Wu–

111
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,000
Crown Prince Wuji?

112
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:58,000
I can't say it, but you can make a wild guess.

113
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,900
Then all right. Just put them here.

114
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:01,400
- Thanks, thanks, thanks.
- All right.

115
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,940
- Older Sis Fuyao.
- Just focusing on joining in on the fun

116
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:05,200
and you've forgotten what you should do again.

117
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:07,830
I'll do it myself.

118
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:14,000
This doctor's medicines are really hard to drink.

119
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:18,400
Older Sis Fuyao, you say, who sent these presents?

120
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:21,800
Anyway, it's not from you nor from that hateful doctor.

121
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:25,100
It is indeed from Crown Prince Wuji.

122
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:27,000
Things that others couldn't obtain, he just casually—

123
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,800
What are you saying?

124
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,900
Crown Prince Wuji.

125
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:35,670
Or Xuanyuan Min.

126
00:08:36,810 --> 00:08:38,330
Who are you talking about?

127
00:08:38,330 --> 00:08:40,540
I don't understand.

128
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:45,600
Then... what about these presents?

129
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,200
Do we throw them away?

130
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,000
Don't.

131
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:52,200
There's a use for them.

132
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,900
- Slowly. Hold it well. This one's good.
- Thank you!

133
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:57,700
- Everyone will get one. Don't push.
- Give me some.

134
00:08:57,700 --> 00:09:00,100
- Everyone will get one. Don't push.
- Thanks!

135
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:01,970
Don't push. Everyone will get one.

136
00:09:01,970 --> 00:09:04,000
- Come one by one. Slower.
- Don't push.

137
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,600
This is for you. Don't push. Everyone gets to have one.

138
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:13,000
Come, slowly.

139
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,300
Tie Cheng, why are you just standing there?

140
00:09:19,170 --> 00:09:20,810
This... is a very good one.

141
00:09:20,810 --> 00:09:22,380
It's made of gold. This...

142
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:24,200
There's a purple phoenix on it.

143
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:27,800
My mother said that it might look very pretty if you put it on.

144
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,000
Everyone will have one! Don't rush!

145
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,600
Here... For you.

146
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:34,000
Slowly! Everyone will get one!

147
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,900
Here. Hold it well.

148
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:40,300
Now, Fuyao has taken over the magistrate position of Yao City and holds the city's military power.

149
00:09:40,300 --> 00:09:41,600
She ordered the repair of the whole city,

150
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:45,000
group training, and plans to organize a citizen soldier troop.

151
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,400
Use them to fight against the troublesome Black Tribe Gang bandits.

152
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:50,600
She's very energetic and deeply indulged in pleasure.

153
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:53,300
It's just that... if you still don't rush here,

154
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:56,600
she might really forget about Wuji.

155
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,600
I heard that the Saintess of Plough, Folian,

156
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:22,700
went to Fufeng to practice Buddhism and do good deeds.

157
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,000
Your traveling around these past years and

158
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:36,200
swiftly moving from place to place is also an advantage.

159
00:10:37,090 --> 00:10:40,970
Now, even if they are unable to find your whereabouts,

160
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,740
no one will find it strange.

161
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:45,200
Am I right?

162
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:50,680
If the Saintess really does encounter a misfortune,

163
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:55,200
it can only be considered as a mysterious case.

164
00:10:57,550 --> 00:11:03,720
Could you really be that ruthless?

165
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:11,240
Showing any mercy to a ruthless person is also doing a bad deed.

166
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:19,000
Weren't all these because I love you?

167
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,800
I missed you.

168
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:24,200
I am not worthy of it.

169
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,900
I'm unable to bear it.

170
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:29,400
I'm just going to ask you one question.

171
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:33,100
Are you canceling this engagement or not?

172
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:54,270
Plough's Queen Heir, Folian, prioritized the world and the citizens.

173
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:59,630
With the consideration that in Five Regions, there are still wars, starving citizens,

174
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:02,780
and people who worry and in wretched poverty,

175
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:07,860
she can't endure to disregard these disasters and attempt to enjoy happiness.

176
00:12:07,860 --> 00:12:11,900
Folian especially chose to sacrifice the marital alliance between Megrez and Plough

177
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:16,550
and is just focusing on meditating and praying for the citizens.

178
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:22,530
If this continues, our brothers of Black Tribe Gang will be starving to death.

179
00:12:22,530 --> 00:12:24,220
What kind of thing is that Fu gal?

180
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:26,190
How come she's this capable?

181
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:30,530
We'll know once we meet her.

182
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:41,840
You can't go! What kind of place is Black Tribe Gang?

183
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,220
You won't be able to come back!

184
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:44,970
Chigui never had any good intentions.

185
00:12:44,970 --> 00:12:46,180
What is possible if he asks you to go there for a talk?

186
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:47,890
This is clearly a trap to harm you!

187
00:12:47,890 --> 00:12:49,470
What you said is reasonable.

188
00:12:49,470 --> 00:12:52,010
Those Black Tribe Gang criminals are cold and ruthless.

189
00:12:52,010 --> 00:12:54,450
They might sound courteous in that invitation,

190
00:12:54,450 --> 00:12:58,210
but this clearly is a Hongmen Banquet for you.

191
00:12:58,210 --> 00:13:00,300
Mister Zong...

192
00:13:00,300 --> 00:13:02,050
Let her decide.

193
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:04,470
I'm just a doctor.

194
00:13:04,470 --> 00:13:06,390
Don't...

195
00:13:07,690 --> 00:13:09,800
I got it.

196
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:15,130
This invitation was made from rabbit skin.

197
00:13:15,130 --> 00:13:16,750
This is a rare item!

198
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:19,040
You mustn't go to Black Tribe Gang!

199
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,630
Why can't I go?

200
00:13:20,630 --> 00:13:25,450
I made so many grand movements here before I was able to receive this invitation.

201
00:13:25,450 --> 00:13:27,580
Just because you say so, I won't go?

202
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:29,820
But you still have not fully recovered from your injuries.

203
00:13:29,820 --> 00:13:33,740
If you fight with others now, won't they be at an advantage?

204
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:36,710
Can others take advantage of me that easily?

205
00:13:36,710 --> 00:13:41,280
If I go there, we still don't know who will be getting whose advantage.

206
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:44,360
No... You can't go. Mister Zong will also not let you go.

207
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:47,230
Right, Mister Zong? Mister Zong!

208
00:13:47,230 --> 00:13:49,590
Can't you see that Mister Zong isn't minding you?

209
00:13:49,590 --> 00:13:53,350
Just stay here and guard our house.

210
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:56,130
- This Black Tribe Gang...
- Mister Zong, try to dissuade her.

211
00:13:56,130 --> 00:13:58,290
I'm surely going.

212
00:13:58,290 --> 00:14:00,800
I really want to take a look at it.

213
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,540
At this late hour, where is Official Fu going?

214
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:12,380
This night scenery is good. I want to go out of the city to admire the moon.

215
00:14:12,380 --> 00:14:13,980
Today is the new moon.

216
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:15,410
There is no moon scenery.

217
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:18,940
With the way you're dressed, you must be attending a banquet. Right?

218
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,780
You just won't disappear.

219
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:26,070
The thing I hate the most is meddling into other people's business, especially yours.

220
00:14:26,070 --> 00:14:28,400
If not because someone entrusted you to me and I made an oath, I wouldn't—

221
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:31,590
Hey, enough! Stop talking.

222
00:14:31,590 --> 00:14:34,040
Just come with us if you want to.

223
00:14:46,420 --> 00:14:50,920
[Black Tribe Gang]

224
00:15:26,310 --> 00:15:28,240
[Black Tribe Gang]

225
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:54,570
Your martial arts skills are not bad.

226
00:17:33,610 --> 00:17:35,650
Official Fu, be careful!

227
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:45,420
Official Fu?

228
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:58,930
I never thought that Official Fu would personally come here.

229
00:17:58,930 --> 00:18:02,480
I thought it's some martial arts master that trespassed our lair.

230
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:05,060
Official Fu indeed has great fighting skills.

231
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:09,200
If I offended you earlier, I hope you can forgive me.

232
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:12,030
It's okay. Please forgive me for my actions, too.

233
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:17,810
Just flowery fists and fancy footworks, we've embarrassed ourselves in front of you.

234
00:18:17,810 --> 00:18:23,590
Since Official Fu came to our place for the first time, we should express some hospitality.

235
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:26,330
Bring it in!

236
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:37,330
Just a small token. Not enough to show my respect for you.

237
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:48,800
I am a very useless person.

238
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:51,950
Whenever I see gold, I just can't proceed.

239
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:57,800
This color...

240
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:02,680
First Boss is really very generous.

241
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,860
You two take these.

242
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:05,800
We should share the wealth.

243
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:15,790
Official Fu said it right.

244
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:19,980
As long as we are united, there are still a lot of chances to get rich in the future.

245
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:24,280
Gold is really a good thing.

246
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:30,330
But... even if I'm greedy, it's within the bounds of morality.

247
00:19:30,330 --> 00:19:35,260
Evil money like this obtained from killing, arson, and stealing,

248
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:39,440
feels hot when held in my hands.

249
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:49,200
Since I've become the magistrate of Yao City,

250
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:52,610
I will then not allow anyone to bully my citizens.

251
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:56,780
If everyone doesn't want to give me this honor,

252
00:19:56,780 --> 00:20:00,210
I must then do things based on the rules of Megrez.

253
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:11,030
Our Black Tribe Gang survived how many Yao City magistrates in these past ten-some years?

254
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:16,300
