275
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:09,830
Whoever drops first must listen to the other party.

276
00:22:09,830 --> 00:22:11,590
Am I right?

277
00:22:12,980 --> 00:22:17,580
Official Fu, do you want to compete in drinking alcohol?

278
00:22:17,580 --> 00:22:22,610
